headline: GTA Online
subtitle: On The Diamond Casino Podium: Annis Savestra
content:
Spin the Lucky Wheel and walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, accessories, snacks, mystery prizes, and — if you’re really lucky — the keys to the Annis Savestra whirling atop the podium nearby.

Discover the Lucky Wheel in The Diamond Casino & Resort lobby. If you win the top prize, your Podium Vehicle will be delivered to your selected Garage.
